      <subsection commented="no" display-inline="no-display-inline" id="idD80BE501CA2A4A67A7F32BF7EF29DBAB">
        <enum>(d)</enum>
        <header>Effective date</header>
        <text>The amendments made by this section shall apply to oil and petroleum products received or entered
			 during calendar quarters beginning more than 60 days after the date of the
			 enactment of this Act.</text>
      </subsection>
    </section>
